text: Kattakkada Assembly Constituency is one of the divisions of Kerala Legislative Assembly within the Thiruvananthapuram district in the Indian state of Kerala. Major communities living there are Nadars (40,000) and Nairs (55,000). As of the 2016 assembly elections, the current MLA is I. B.
